channel.description: [IMG]http://i67.photobucket.com/albums/h313/googleit2/recentsig.jpg[/img] Some notes on it...the render is actually at 100%, I only remembered it didn't have to be in black and white (I was half asleep when I made it), and it is almost purely defaults, I used 3 brushes in it. Now that I look at it, I realize I forgot to put my name on it...oh well, if anyone wants it, I'll post the .psd because I'm too lazy to open PS again...Anyways, rate /10
